sentence: how many people live in the capital of texas ?
sentence-with-vars: how many people live in the capital of state0 ?
sql: select city.population from city where city.city_name = ( select state.capital from state where state.state_name = ' texas ' ) ;
sql-with-vars: select city.population from city where city.city_name = ( select state.capital from state where state.state_name = ' state0 ' ) ;
